                <!-- Intro Section -->
                <div class="intro-section">
                    <p>Are you planning an intrastate move in Chicago, the surrounding suburbs or throughout Illinois?
                        At New City Moving, we provide affordable local moving services for homeowners and businesses.
                        Our team takes care of all your crucial relocation needs, from secure packing to unloading at
                        your new destination. For expert support with an intrastate move, contact us today for your free
                        quote.</p>

                    <p>An intrastate move is a relocation that takes place entirely within the same state, such as
                        moving from Chicago to another city or area within Illinois. Since 2009, the team at New City
                        Moving has planned and delivered in-state moves for homeowners, tenants, college students,
                        office managers and many others.</p>

                    <p>As a licensed and insured intrastate moving company, your belongings are in good hands with our
                        professional relocation team. We offer secure packing and unpacking services, expert loading and
                        unloading, optional storage, specialty item handling and well-planned logistics.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- What to Expect Section -->
                <section>
                    <h2>What to Expect From an Interstate Move</h2>
                    <p>Moving within Illinois requires careful planning and coordination. Our local crews are familiar
                        with Illinois routes and regulations, ensuring on-time delivery whether you're moving across
                        town or across the state. With competitive pricing and transparent estimates, you'll have the
                        clear costs you need to plan your move with confidence.</p>

                    <div class="service-grid">
                        <div class="service-card">
                            <h4><span class="service-icon">🗺️</span> In-State Expertise</h4>
                            <p>Our crews know Illinois roads, traffic patterns, and local regulations to ensure
                                efficient delivery anywhere in the state.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="service-card">
                            <h4><span class="service-icon">📋</span> Comprehensive Planning</h4>
                            <p>We create detailed moving plans that account for distances, access points, and timing to
                                streamline your relocation.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="service-card">
                            <h4><span class="service-icon">💰</span> Transparent Pricing</h4>
                            <p>Receive clear, upfront pricing with no hidden fees so you can budget accurately for your
                                intrastate move.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="service-card">
                            <h4><span class="service-icon">🛡️</span> Licensed & Insured</h4>
                            <p>As a fully licensed Illinois moving company, we provide insurance coverage and
                                professional handling for peace of mind.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- What We Move Section -->
                <section>
                    <h2>What We Typically Move in an Interstate Relocation</h2>
                    <p>Our full-service moving solutions cover everything you need for a comfortable and convenient
                        intrastate relocation. Here's just a small selection of the items we regularly transport.</p>

                    <div class="items-list">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Household belongings, like clothes, furniture and electronics</li>
                            <li>Bulky items, such as dining tables, exercise equipment and pianos</li>
                            <li>Refrigerators, washers, dryers and dishwashers</li>
                            <li>Valuable possessions, including artwork and antiques</li>
                            <li>Office chairs, furniture and IT equipment</li>
                            <li>Outdoor items, like grills and patio furniture</li>
                            <li>Musical instruments and sound equipment</li>
                            <li>Sports equipment and hobby collections</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <p>We'll handle all your home and business items for your statewide move, ensuring that everything
                        arrives just as it left. And when you're not ready to receive all of your belongings right away,
                        we offer secure storage solutions for both short-term and long-term needs.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Services Included Section -->
                <section>
                    <h2>Comprehensive Interstate Moving Services</h2>
                    <p>At New City Moving, we understand that every intrastate move has unique requirements. That's why
                        we offer a complete range of services to customize your relocation experience and ensure a
                        smooth transition to your new location.</p>

