                <!-- FAQ Section -->
                <section class="faq-section">
                    <h2>Common Questions About Interstate Moving</h2>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>Can I pack my own belongings for an intrastate move?</span>
                            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <div class="faq-answer-content">
                                Reputable intrastate moving companies allow you to pack your own belongings for a
                                relocation. Customers can choose between self-packing, partial packing, or letting the
                                movers pack everything with full-service packing. However, when you want to protect
                                fragile items and save time during a relocation, it's a good idea to choose a full
                                packing service.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>Can intrastate moves be completed on the same day?</span>
                            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <div class="faq-answer-content">
                                Most intrastate moves can be completed in a single day, since the distance is limited to
                                within state lines. However, same-day completion may not be possible for larger moves,
                                or those that span the full length of the state. Your moving coordinator will provide an
                                accurate timeline during your consultation.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>Can intrastate movers transport fragile items safely?</span>
                            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <div class="faq-answer-content">
                                Professional intrastate movers have the expertise and materials to safely transport
                                fragile items. We use specialized packing materials, custom crating for valuable items,
                                and careful handling techniques to ensure your delicate possessions arrive intact.
                                Insurance coverage is also available for additional protection.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>How much does an intrastate move in Illinois cost?</span>
                            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <div class="faq-answer-content">
                                The cost of an intrastate move depends on several factors including distance, volume of
                                belongings, services required, and timing. On average, local moves within Illinois range
                                from a few hundred to several thousand dollars. Contact us for a free, no-obligation
                                quote tailored to your specific moving needs.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>Do I need to be present during the entire move?</span>
                            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <div class="faq-answer-content">
                                While it's recommended to be present at both the pickup and delivery locations to
                                oversee the inventory and provide instructions, you don't necessarily need to be there
                                for the entire process. You can designate a trusted representative to be present on your
                                behalf if needed.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
